OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScotland's drug deaths     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftotal down for first time  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fin eight years             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of people who died of drug  
OL,6, misuse in Scotland last year dropped   
OL,7, slightly to 1,330 - the first time the 
OL,8, figure has been down in eight years.   
OL,10,FNational Records for Scotland (NRS)    
OL,11,Fstatistics showed there were nine fewer
OL,12,Fdeaths than the 1,339 recorded the     
OL,13,Fprevious year.                         
OL,15,FHowever, Scotland continues to have by 
OL,16,Ffar the highest drug death rate        
OL,17,Frecorded by any country in Europe.     
OL,19,FThe upward trend had been accelerating 
OL,20,Fsince 2013.                            
